Now when you copy the table data, the format will be:
```
First Text[TAB][TAB]Number[TAB]Date[TAB]Second Text
```

This extra tab between First Text and Number columns will create additional spacing when you paste the data into Google Sheets, making it easier to distinguish between these two columns.

